title: Bozo on 10 Years in Prison, Calls Out Tyga, Mr Capone-E Beef & More
description:
Bozo sits down with Doknow and drops tons of gems! From sharing his come up, losing his mom, having a strong family unit, his new music, Tyga's song and more.

-----
00:00 Intro
3:15 Getting to the streets right after he lost his mom
8:09 Arrested for attempted m*rder and arm robberies, did 10 years instead of 35
9:36 The 35 years sentence moment
12:40 Went on the run for 4 months, caught in Colorado
14:31 The girl he was with, her mom snitched on him
15:28 Got picked up at the house, playing video games with his girl's son
23:56 Doing 10 years, lost his confidence but his sisters helped a lot, women are the foundation of everything
26:30 Rekindling his rap career after coming out of jail
27:40 His mom never bought him toys, she used to buy him rap tapes like Ice Cube, EPMD, etc
29:00 His close friend built him a room coz he was sleeping on his sister's couch
30:45 Parting ways with his initial label, Bozo was then blackballed
33:53 Bozo says it's mandatory for men to challenge each other and elevate each other
34:30 "You wanna find a p____ MF look at your phone, anyone with a g*n on social media is a p____"
35:30 Fave rappers: LL Cool J, Ice Cube
36:35 Wishing the best to his prior label, says he will talk to Capone eventually
36:59 "You don't have to forgive everyone, you have to keep a record of betrayed!! Forgiving is encouraging a nasty behavior"
39:30 Performing with Prayers July 30
42:19 Working with Benny the Butcher
46:36 Bozo gives his take on Doknow's viral Tyga moment, says Doknow will learn a lot from this
47:51 Bozo has a message for Tyga: "you lost your pass, it's revoked"
48:31 Bozo says Tyga is not coming back from it, he's making fun of a whole culture for profit
49:41 Says it's deeper than Tyga, you should inspire somebody
51:25 Doknow and Bozo react to the Tyga backlash
54:14 If anything, Tyga lit fire under the community's *ss, it was a necessary moment, but this was bound to happen, boundaries need to be set
54:54 Bozo's top 5 right now
57:37 Bozo calls out Hispanic media for not speaking out on issues
-----
